text: Itheum fuscoantennale is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1943. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Itheum fuscoantennale. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1943
